# 健康检查（Gateway 白名单，免 JWT）
# GET /api/auth/ping、/api/admin/ping、/api/gallery/ping、/api/monitor/health
@gateway = http://127.0.0.1:8888

### @name authPing
GET {{gateway}}/api/auth/ping
Accept: application/json

### @name adminPing
GET {{gateway}}/api/admin/ping
Accept: application/json

### @name galleryPing
GET {{gateway}}/api/gallery/ping
Accept: application/json

### @name screenplayPing
GET {{gateway}}/api/screenplay/ping
Accept: application/json

### @name replyPing
GET {{gateway}}/api/reply/ping
Accept: application/json

### @name monitorHealth
GET {{gateway}}/api/monitor/health
Accept: application/json
